ended and much publicised auction. In order to fulfill this dream, he recruits five men - all resembling the President of India, and asks them to undergo vigorous training in order to take over as the President. That done, he selects one of them, Nathuram, eliminates the other four, and arranges the kidnapping of the President, with success. He than implants Nathuram as the President - and the stage is set for the biggest auction in Earth\'s history - when India will be auctioned to the highest bidder.',160,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDAxMDhmNTUtZDllMS00MGYyLWIyYTEtMzE3NWQ1NjdlYjJjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTE0MDc0NTM@.jpg',1995,'Comedy','Hindi','Ketan Mehta','Parvati Balagopalan, Ketan Mehta, Deepa Sahi',NULL,'Ranjit Barot','W.B. Rao','Jeethu Mandal'),('Guddu',4,'Guddu Bahadur meets fellow collegian, Salina Gupta and both fall in love with each other. Then one day both meet in a vehicle accident resulting in Salina losing her sight; Guddu holds himself responsible for this outrage and is restricted by Salina\'s family not to meet with her again. Although Salina does not consider Guddu guilty she does not want to meet with him and be a burden on him. Shortly after Guddu find out that he is diagnosed with brain tumor and does not have long to live so he decides to donate his eyes to Salina after his death but this is not agreeable by Guddu\'s advocate father, Vikram which forces Guddu to move to court in order to ascertain his rights. Ultimately this decision not only affects his dear ones but changes lives forever.',160,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTYxNDYxNzY4N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDM2ODgzMQ@@.jpg',1995,'Drama, Romance','Hindi','Prem Lalwani','Abrar Alvi, Abrar Alvi, Prem Lalwani, Prem Lalwani, Prem Lalwani','Prem Lalwani, Vivek Lalwani','Sunil Kaushik, Naushad','V. Durga Prasad','Mohan Kaul'),('Zamaana Deewana',4.7,'With crime flourishing out of control, the Assistant Commissioner of Police (ACP) arranges a meeting of senior police officers to discus