er hand is a prankster, not taking life seriously at all enjoying life with his friends among whom is Anjali (Ayesha Jhulka) who loves him silently. Sanju however turns his attention on the new girl on the block, Devika (Pooja Bedi) and convinces her he is rich. He uses the money his father has asked him to deposit in the bank to buy a costly necklace for Devika instead. When his father finds out, he chucks Sanju out of the house. At the annual college dance competition when Devika finds out that Sanju is from Model and poor, she dumps him turning her attention to Shekhar. All through Anjali is a silent pillar of support for Sanju. Shekhar and his friends injure Ratan, almost killing him to keep him out of the race. It is at this point that Sanju realizes he has to get serious and responsible in life and he enters the cycle race to do what a man must do...',174,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTU1ZjQwNDAtZDAwMC00OTcyLTg4MDUtOTUwYTU4N2M4YTgxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDUzOTQ5MjY@.jpg',1992,'Comedy, Drama, Romance, Sport','Hindi, English','Mansoor Khan','Nasir Hussain, Mansoor Khan, Mansoor Khan','Nasir Hussain','Jatin Pandit, Lalit Pandit','Najeeb Khan','Dilip Kotalgi, Zafar Sultan'),('Dil Hai Ke Manta Nahin',7.2,'Pooja, a rich and spoilt child, runs away from the yacht of her dad for her love- a movie star. On her way to mumbai (bombay in this film), she meets Raghu (amir khan) in a bus, and soon has to rely on him for the safe arrival of hers to mumbai. Raghu has money in his mind. He has a plan to get rich, but love strikes them and they both fall for each other...',154,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTFiNGZiMWMtZDBhNC00ODVlLWEyOTctM2E3Y2VhMjA4MjAwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1991,'Adventure, Comedy, Drama, Musical, Romance','Hindi','Mahesh Bhatt','Robin Bhatt, Robin Bhatt, Sharad Joshi','Mukesh Bhatt, Gulshan Kumar','Shravan Rathod, Nadeem Saifi','Pravin Bhatt','Sanjay Sankla'),('Afsana Pyar Ka',5.3,'Animosity has existed between the families of Raj 