erchants then decide to take help of British to drive out Khameran\'s from their region where they offer them 5000 gold coins.Shamshera and Khameran overcome the Britishers who flee from the region but Daroga Shudh Singh comes with message from British that Khameran \'s will be given a better life if they surrender to British,Shamshera and his community reach the fort where they realize that Shudha Singh has laid a trap for them and they are kept as slaves in the fort the British ask Shamshera to give them 10,000 gold coin\'s and free his community.In order to free his people Shamshera decides to elope from a secret place and gather the gold but gets caught and is killed in front of his community by and posed as traitor.25 years later his son Bali to believes his father was a traitor and wants to join army of Shudh Singh where he is asked to beat a child but he sacrifices himself to Shudh Singh in place of child and learns from his father\'s friend Pir Baba that how his father scarified his life for their community.Bali escapes from the secret hide as guided by Pir Baba an reaches a village where few Khameran \'s are living a different identity since years Shamshera had left few people behind as he was aware Shudh Singh will betray them.The Khameran left behind still live with a hope of freedom and team up with Bali and a dancer Sona an make life of upper caste people hell again by making them realize that Shamshera is back.',178,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODVlNWNmN2EtYWJlYy00ZTc5LThjMTItYTQ0ZTlmZDYwN2VjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTkzNDQ4ODc@.jpg',2022,'Action, Adventure, Drama','Hindi','Karan Malhotra','Khila Bisht, Karan Malhotra, Piyush Mishra, Neelesh Misra, Ekta Pathak Malhotra','Aditya Chopra, Sudhanshu Kumar, Bharat Rawail','Mithun Sharma','Anay Goswami','Shivkumar V. Panicker'),('Sharmaji Namkeen',7.7,'B. G. Sharma is a 58-year old widower, and a middle-class man, living in West Delhi. One fine day, the company he has worked for his entire life lays him off. Sharma struggles to cope with this beast called retirement. He keeps finding ways to stay relevant but only ends up getting in his two sons\' ways. The only time he really comes into his own is when he is in the kitchen. He is a cook nonpareil, waiting to be discovered, not yet fully aware of his culinary superpower.',119,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BY2MxNjVlNjMtOGExMi00NWRjLThhYzQtNDY4OWZkMzcwNjhiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTI1NDEyNTM5.jpg',2022,'Comedy, Drama, Family','Hindi','Hitesh Bhatia','Hitesh Bhatia, Supratik Sen','Farhan Akhtar, Abhishek Chaubey, Kassim Jagmagia, Chetana Kowshik, Niraj Kumar Pandey, Vishal Ramchandani, Ayush Saini, Ravi Sarin, Ritesh Sidhwani, Honey Trehan','Sneha Khanwalkar','Piyush Puty, Harendra Singh','Bodhaditya Banerjee'),('Smile',NULL,'After witnessing a bizarre, traumatic incident involving a patient, Dr. Rose Cotter starts experiencing frightening occurrences that she can\'t explain. Rose must confront her troubling past in order to survive and escape her horrifying new reality.',NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODJkNDY0MDgtYzFmYy00YzMyLThiNGUtOGI3ZjcyNjk0MWFiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODc0OTEyNDU@.jpg',2022,'Horror','English','Parker Finn','Parker Finn','Marty Bowen, Wyck Godfrey, Isaac Klausner, Robert Salerno','Cristobal Tapia de Veer','Charlie Sarroff','Elliot Greenberg'),('Sanju',7.6,'Few lives in our time are as dramatic and enigmatic as the saga of Sanjay Dutt. Coming from a family of cinema legends, he himself became a film star, then saw dizzying heights and darkest depths: adulation of die-hard fans, unending battles with various addictions, brushes with the underworld, prison terms, loss of loved ones, and the haunting speculation that he might be a terrorist. Sanju is in turns a hilarious and heartbreaking exploration of one man\'s battle against his own wild self and the formidable external forces trying to crush him. It depicts the journey of a man through everything that life can throw at him. Some true stori