d and is now living a wealthy, happy life as the Mayor of that town. But nothing is the same for Kailash as his wife Savitri and Kishan are untraceable. Meanwhile Kishan goes to Khurana\'s bungalow to bring his wife Sanam home; what he finds is a very stubborn, spoiled, and rude Sanam, who is not willing to go with him. Kishan then forcefully brings her to his mother. Unknown to both, Sanam has a surprise for both mother and son.',156,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWY5MzhkNWYtODE5Zi00NGRiLWI3OWItNWY5MGFhMDRkMWVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTE0MDc0NTM@.jpg',1994,'Drama, Romance','Hindi','Shomu Mukherjee','Anwar Khan, Tanveer Khan, Shomu Mukherjee','Shomu Mukherjee','Anand Chitragupth, Milind Chitragupth','Aloke Dasgupta','Vishwanath Rao'),('Chaand Kaa Tukdaa',3.8,'Shyam lives a wealthy lifestyle in London, England; he\'s considered one of the 10 richest people in the world. His father, S.K. Malhotra, was killed, and his mother identified his killer, but before this person could be apprehended, she herself passes away, but not before asking Shyam to return to India and get married to a beautiful girl. Shyam does return to India, and once there does meet the girl, Radha, of his dreams, but does not know that Radha is a mere pawn in the hands of a group of people, including his father\'s killer, who are after his wealth and estate, and will do anything in their power to obtain it.',155,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWRlOGVhNzYtOTBkZi00NmY2LTgxMmQtNzYyNDgxMTliZTI1XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1994,'Action, Comedy, Crime, Drama, Romance','Hindi','Saawan Kumar Tak','Sachin Bhowmick, Anwar Khan, Saawan Kumar Tak','Saawan Kumar Tak','Kishore Sharma, Mahesh Sharma','G. Shyam Kumar','Jawahar Razdan'),('Hum Aapke Hain Koun...!',7.5,'Prem, a top student, is learning the ropes of business under his elder brother Rajesh and his uncle Kailashnath, a big industrialist. In another town, Nisha is studying computer science and is the darling of her elder sister, Pooja, and her parents, Professor Choudhry and Kamladevi. Fate brings the two families together and this results in the the betrothal of Rajesh and Pooja. At the wedding, Prem meets Nisha and falls in love with this carefree woman. With Pooja as the woman of the house, joy knows no bounds in Prem\'s family. Months pass by and Pooja becomes pregnant. Nisha is invited to come and stay with her sister and attend the traditional function before the child\'s birth. Nisha\'s arrival is like a dream come true for Prem. Nisha stays there until the birth of the child, taking over the household chores, and becoming very much a part of the family. In soft whispers, Prem and Nisha commit their love for each other and secretly dream of spending a lifetime together. Then fate strikes a cruel blow when Pooja dies after a sudden fall down a flight of stairs. Because of this tragedy, life in the house comes to a standstill. Rajesh worries about the future of his motherless child, and it causes his health to deteriorate. Nisha\'s father suggests that Nisha should get married to Rajesh and become the mother of Pooja\'s child. Prem and Nisha decide to sacrifice their love for the sake of the family. Fate intervenes once again when Rajesh comes to know the truth behind Prem and Nisha\'s sacrifice. Putting his child into Nisha\'s arms, Rajesh unites and blesses the two lovers, whose hearts long to belong together.',206,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjc0ODAwMmItMmQwMy00MmRmLThjOGYtZGEwYjQ2ZjcyYzA3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',1994,'Comedy, Drama, Musical, Romance','Hindi','Sooraj R. Barjatya','Sooraj R. Barjatya, Sooraj R. Barjatya','Ajit Kumar Barjatya, Kamal Kumar Barjatya, Rajat A. Barjatya, Rajkumar Barjatya, Sooraj R. Barjatya','Vijay Patil','Rajan Kinagi','Mukhtar Ahmed'),('Bulund',4.8,'A blind lover is on revenge on the killer who raped and killed his love.',132,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjRjY2QzY2QtMjM4My00MTFjLTk1ZjItMjBlYTM1MTg3OGNjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjQ2MDI5OD