s him as Rajesh, although she has some misgivings. Rajesh\'s dog and cook realise what has happened, so Jackoss kills them so they can\'t expose him. The authorities are also less trusting and do not allow Jackoss to enter the high-security zone until some other criminals help Jackoss to convince the authorities of his identity. Meanwhile Rajesh escapes and makes his way back to India. Jackoss had plans to blow up a laboratory, but Rajesh reaches it on time and foils his plan. After killing Jackoss, Rajesh marries Rita.',138,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzA4YzVlMDgtNjNiMS00NjllLWE5OTQtYmY3ZmU1YzQ0Njk4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTM3MDMyMDQ@.jpg',1969,'Action, Crime, Romance, Thriller, Mystery','Hindi','Brij','Javed Akhtar, Deven Verma, Deven Verma','Deven Verma','Jaikishan Dayabhai Panchal, Shankarsingh Raghuwanshi','Anwar Siraj','Hrishikesh Mukherjee'),('Asambhav',3.7,'Adit, played by Arjun Rampal, is in the Indian army. When the Indian president is kidnapped, Adit is sent undercover to rescue the president and his daughter. Adit becomes a journalist for IndiaTimes, and manages to make his way to Switzerland with the help of a police officer called Bhatnagar. On the flight, Adit meets Alisha (Priyanka Chopra). Alysia is a singer, and has come to Switzerland under a contract in order to do a show with Sam Hams. Her friend Shilpa accompanies her. However the people who Alysia and Shilpa have come to Switzerland with, are drug smugglers. Shilpa is murdered when she finds this out, and Alysia pretends she knows nothing. She meets up with Adit, and together they help each other. In the end, Adit saves the president and Alysia is able to go back to India with Adit.',139,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTRjZmI0YzgtNTQwNC00Mjc3LWFlOGQtZDZlZjk5NzkxMDg0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',2004,'Action, Adventure, Drama, Thriller','Hindi','Rajiv Rai','Rajiv Rai, Naeem Sha, Naeem Sha','Ashwani Chopra, Gulshan Rai','Viju Shah','Sukumar Jatania, Sukumar','Taranjiet Singh N