ery, Thriller','Hindi','Sujoy Ghosh','Sujoy Ghosh, Sujoy Ghosh, Sujoy Ghosh, Advaita Kala, Suresh Nair, Ritesh Shah, Sutapa Sikdar, Nikhil Vyas','Mohammed Attarwala, Jyoti Kapur Das, Saubhik Das, Dhaval Gada, Kushal Gada, Sujoy Ghosh, Vikram Malhotra, Suresh Nair, Arindam Sil, Rukshana Tabassum','Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani','Satyajit Pande','Namrata Rao'),('Urumi: The Warriors Who Wanted to Kill Vasco Da Gama',7,'Chirakkal Kelu Nayanar, a warrior in 16th century Kerala wants to avenge his father killed in a confrontation with Vasco da Gama and his troops and is assisted by his best friend Vavvali and warrior princess Ayesha.',172,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjkzMWFiZmUtMWQyYy00NzRhLThiNjItY2RiYTUzNWZmNDhkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDY5MTUyNjU@.jpg',2011,'Action, Drama','Malayalam, Portuguese, English','Santosh Sivan','Shankar Ramakrishnan','Muvoz Creations, Kyoko Dan, Suri Gopalan, Paul Hardart, Doug Mankoff, Shaji Nadesan, Mubina Rattonsey, Santosh Sivan, Glamour Still, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Milind Vereker','Deepak Dev','Santosh Sivan','A. Sreekar Prasad'),('No One Killed Jessica',7.2,'Devastated when she is told that that her sister, Jessica Lall, is shot dead by Manish Bhardwaj, the son of Pramod, a Congress party Member of Parliament in Haryana, Delhi-based Sabrina Lall, in the company of her parents, attends the Court to view a charade that will lead to the acquittal of the accused and his accomplices seven years after the incident. Disillusioned by rampart police corruption and inefficiency; a stagnant British introduced legal system; the passing of her mother & the hospitalization of her father, she retreats unto herself. Then foul-mouthed NDTV employee, Meera Gaity, known for being more of an activist than a Journalist, takes an interest in this incident, and uncovers conspiracy & corruption that led to the accused\' acquittals - leading to a near India-wide protest. While preparing herself to participate in a candle-lit procession at Delhi\'s India Gate, Meera will confront Sabrina and will come to know the reasons why the latter refuses to be involved in this situation any more.',136,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU4Mzk0NDY3OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjE1MTkyNA@@.jpg',2011,'Biography, Crime, Drama, Thriller','Hindi, English','Raj Kumar Gupta','Amitabh Bhattacharya, Raj Kumar Gupta','Aditi Anand, Vikas Bahl, Rakesh Bhagwani, Manish Hariprasad, Siddharth Roy Kapur, Shakir Ali Khan, Deven Khote, Zarina Mehta, Rucha Pathak, Ajay Rai, Aviv Screwvala, Ronnie Screwvala, Shubh Shivdasani, Shamsher Walia','Amit Trivedi','Anay Goswami','Aarti Bajaj'),('Karadi Tales',NULL,'The Karadi Tales Animation episodes feature stories from the Panchatantra, the Jataka, and from the phenomenal regional folklore of Bharat, narrated by master storytellers like Naseeruddin Shah, Girish Karnad, Saeed Jefferey, Usha Uthup, Vidya Balan, Boman Irani, Javed Jaffrey, Rahul Dravid - The character design is based on the rich visual traditions of Bharat - the puppet traditions, the Gondh, the Warli, and the myriad imageries of our land and rendered in a unique animation style inspired by Indian mask making and puppetry cultures. Textured with vibrant music and songs based on Bharatiya Shastriya Sangeet, Karadi Tales is the ultimate experience in storytelling.',NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmUyNDhkOTctZDJjYy00MzFjLWI2YmEtNTc5Njk1MmU0M2RkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjg4MDQ0NDc@.jpg',2010,'Animation','English',NULL,'Shobha Viswanath',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Ishqiya',7.3,'Ishqiya is a story about love arising in characters, portrayed uniquely according to their own personal traits. The situations in the plot lead the characters to experience the emotion creeping into their lives in the most unexpected manner.',118,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTc1Y2EyOWUtNWExMi00OGNkLTkxOGQtNDY0YzYxNTA0OWUxXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyODE5NzE3OTE@.jpg',2010,'Comedy, Drama, Romance, Thriller','Urdu','Abhishek Chaubey','Vishal Bhardwaj, Sabrina Dhawan, Abhis